Class CourseEnrollment

java.lang.Object
com.panotify.model.CourseEnrollment
public class CourseEnrollment extends Object
Represents a student's enrollment in a course within the PaNotify system. Contains information about the enrollment relationship between a student and a course.
Version:
1.0
Author:
PaNotify Team
